# Golden dataset for the M3 significance scorer.
# Format: one GoldenEntry JSON per line. See app.services.eval.schema.
# Comments (#) and blank lines are ignored by the loader.
#
# Rubric bands (keep in sync with app.services.significance.CHANGE_TYPES):
#   typo_or_cosmetic  0.00–0.19
#   minor_wording     0.20–0.39
#   clarification     0.40–0.59
#   substantive       0.60–0.79
#   critical          0.80–1.00
#
# Each entry's `significance_score` range is slightly wider than the
# rubric band so normal LLM drift doesn't false-negative.
#
# Curation notes:
#   - Aim for ~2–3 entries per band once you start getting real traffic.
#   - Use real URLs where possible; synthetic diffs are OK to start.
#   - Prefer locking down categorical fields (change_type, topic)
#     over tight score ranges — classification drift is what hurts users.

